  <original-body>Hello,

@@@
class Tag
  belongs_to :post
  validates_presence_of :post
end

class Post
  has_many :post_tags
  accepts_nested_attribute_for :post_tags
end
@@@

On Post creation save fails because tag's post is not yet set to the new Post id.

In facts, if the validation is removed the save is successful and the post_id is correctly filled in.</original-body>
